@av8ramit There seems to be an issue with the Linux GPU binaries, that I can't figure out. I get the following error when using the GPU prebuilt binaries:

undefined symbol: _ZN10tensorflow12OpDefBuilder4AttrESs

I don't get this error with the CPU binaries. Do you know what may be causing this? Are they both compiled using GCC 4?
body:
@av8ramit There seems to be an issue with the Linux GPU binaries, that I can't figure out. I get the following error when using the GPU prebuilt binaries:

```
undefined symbol: _ZN10tensorflow12OpDefBuilder4AttrESs
```

I don't get this error with the CPU binaries. Do you know what may be causing this? Are they both compiled using GCC 4?
